-shipping $15 NZ or $35 elsewhere (NZD)
-Print is accompanied by certificate of authenticity by artist and the quote/title of painting.

Please contact me if you would like a different size print not specified here.

About Giclée printing:

“Giclée” pronounced, “zhee-clay”, is a French word describing the technology "to spray pigment” resulting in the highest quality reproductions of Fine-Art available in the world. Giclées have great superiority in beauty, quality and durability, lasting up to 120 years before any colour change is apparent to the human eye.
